OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy low cloud at first, but
OL,6,Fthis will soon burn back to the coast
OL,7,Fduring the morning, leaving plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine for the rest of the day.
OL,9,FBreezy northeasterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAreas of low cloud will move
OL,12,Fwestwards from the coast overnight
OL,13,Fwith perhaps some isolated light
OL,14,Fdrizzle, but most areas likely
OL,15,Fremaining dry.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FAnother cloudy start, but
OL,18,Fsimilar to Monday cloud will burn back
OL,19,Ftowards the coast to leave plenty of
OL,20,Fsunny spells for the rest of the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
